title: HUGE CAIR ANDROS SIEGE: New Custom Map - Third Age Total War Reforged Mod Gameplay
description:
HUGE CAIR ANDROS SIEGE - Third Age Total War - Hey guys! Welcome back to another epic Third Age Siege Battle. This is a 4v4 online battle on a new custom Cair Andros map. I command the orcs of the misty mountains and I am ready to fight to the last! Enjoy the Siege Battle :D
